{
  "signal_description": "Calculate the manual reconciled invoice rate as a percentage for each PO item line type. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-545' table. The 'Invoice ID' column is used to count the number of distinct invoices. The 'Last Invoice Reconciliation Status' column is filtered to only include invoices with a status of 'Reconciling'. The 'Last Invoice Submission Method' column is also filtered to only include invoices submitted via 'PaperInvoice'. The count of distinct invoices meeting both filter conditions is divided by the count of distinct invoices meeting only the 'Last Invoice Reconciliation Status' filter condition. The result is then multiplied by 100 to get the percentage. The result is displayed as 'Manual Reconciled Invoice Rate %' along with the 'PO Item Line Type' column."
}
